  "title": "The Last Perfect Game: The Jerry Stephenson Story",
  "description": "In 1963, a regular guy named Jerry Stephenson did the impossible, bowling 12 strikes in a row, the first and last perfect game at Plaza Bowling. Since then the legend has only grown, but who was Jerry? From the creatives behind the Sterling-nominated Talk Treaty to Me (★★★★) and High and Dry (★★★★★) comes a (mostly) true story!",
